1. how can we add external file in it?

Ans:- step1. Make a "public" Folder and inside it make 3 folder "images" , "stylesheets", "javascript" in it.
     step2. use "public" folder in "app.js" and make it static route(/) --> 
     <!-- "app.use(express.static(__dirname + "/public"));" -->
     step3. maake new file "style.css" in "public" -> stylesheets -> style.css and write test code here.
     step4. in "index.ejs" add link tag and use path "/stylesheets/style.css"
 

